This is a great, simple and flavorful recipe...and it tastes even better the second day. The flavors really work well together. I didn't have shallots, so I used yellow onions, minced and it turned out well. I made the potatoes to accompany a pot roast...mmm mmm! Delicious. I will definitely make item again.

