Rating: 3
I have enjoyed this recipe for years. It goes well with a number of different dishes. I have served this at several parties and always received compliments. I tend to increase the amount of basil because it enhances the flavor.

Rating: 3
This recipe was so easy to make, and very tasty! I couldn't find potatoes as small as the recipe suggested, so I cut my 2-inchers into quarters and turned them with a spatula. Had to keep the heat a little lower to prevent over-browning, but they cooked much more quickly than keeping them whole and were absolutely delicious!

